cdata.desc: STRESScoin is a PoW/PoS hybrid that wil change to full PoS.Designed to be a test cryptocurrencywith the purpose offiguring out possible problems and solutionsregarding the coin's current model STS will undergo various stress tests until conclusive results and met, at which point STRESScoin will arrange a swap for STS second generation coin.
